WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.830 --> 01:39.210
[2022]

01:37.870 --> 01:39.400
Okay, I have no problem with that.

01:39.400 --> 01:40.120
Just pay more attention

01:40.120 --> 01:40.840
to this.

01:41.039 --> 01:42.300
And just do it this way.

01:45.680 --> 01:46.280
Mr. Wang.

01:48.680 --> 01:49.280
What is it?

01:49.400 --> 01:50.039
Well...

01:50.350 --> 01:53.479
It's about the collaboration
with Xing Min Technology.

01:54.920 --> 01:56.580
We can't do it this way, right?

01:57.759 --> 01:58.890
Can't do it this way?

01:59.000 --> 01:59.400
Yes.

01:59.509 --> 02:00.840
Then how should we do it?

02:01.120 --> 02:02.080
I entrusted this

02:02.110 --> 02:02.910
to you before.

02:03.840 --> 02:05.100
Did you handle it well?

02:09.100 --> 02:10.240
Okay, look, Xia Xiaolan.

02:10.240 --> 02:11.640
Let me ask you a question.

02:12.840 --> 02:14.800
How long's it been since you graduated?

02:14.800 --> 02:17.000
How long have you been in this industry?

02:17.000 --> 02:17.630
Do you plan

02:17.630 --> 02:18.420
to just keep your head down

02:18.420 --> 02:19.480
and work like this?

02:19.760 --> 02:21.190
Can you please think about

02:21.190 --> 02:22.210
what kind of person

02:22.210 --> 02:22.940
you want to be

02:22.960 --> 02:24.690
and what kind of life you want to live?

02:24.690 --> 02:25.470
Can you even try to be

02:25.470 --> 02:26.600
a bit clear-headed?

02:31.280 --> 02:32.610
What are you looking at?

02:33.120 --> 02:34.650
Are you done with your work?

02:35.120 --> 02:35.470
Fine.

02:35.470 --> 02:37.310
Everyone stays to work overtime tonight.

02:37.310 --> 02:39.040
It's all thanks to Xia Xiaolan.

02:45.000 --> 02:47.820
[Episode 33: What kind of life
do you want?]

02:54.320 --> 02:54.840
You haven't

02:54.840 --> 02:57.100
hit me up in a while, Second Young Master.

03:01.190 --> 03:02.240
Xia Xiaolan and Du Zhaohui

03:02.240 --> 03:03.520
won the competition.

03:03.910 --> 03:05.110
Second Young Master,

03:05.750 --> 03:08.350
are you really going to sit back
and do nothing?

03:09.290 --> 03:10.910
Then, Ms. Vivi, please tell me

03:10.910 --> 03:11.840
what I should do.

03:14.080 --> 03:16.140
I neither have Zhaohui's capability

03:16.400 --> 03:17.710
to win Daddy's favor,

03:19.470 --> 03:21.930
nor can I get pregnant
to secure my position.

03:23.280 --> 03:24.430
What should I do?

03:26.750 --> 03:28.600
Why mock yourself, Second Young Master?

03:28.600 --> 03:29.160
It's just

03:29.190 --> 03:30.520
5% of the shares.

03:31.410 --> 03:32.740
The game isn't over yet.

03:33.490 --> 03:34.400
It's still

03:35.110 --> 03:35.970
anyone's game.

03:44.630 --> 03:45.800
Sometimes I really envy

03:45.800 --> 03:47.260
your innocence, Ms. Vivi.

03:48.430 --> 03:49.590
Do you think Daddy actually cares

03:49.590 --> 03:50.990
about this competition?

03:51.110 --> 03:52.970
He cares about no one but Zhaohui.

03:54.880 --> 03:56.370
Even I, his grown son,

03:56.400 --> 03:57.660
don't mean much to him.

03:59.870 --> 04:01.400
As for the one in your belly,

04:02.710 --> 04:03.970
how much could he care?

04:05.800 --> 04:06.960
Even though Daddy

04:07.940 --> 04:09.050
won't lay a hand

04:09.080 --> 04:10.030
on his own son,

04:11.480 --> 04:12.910
if he finds out that you're

04:12.910 --> 04:14.710
playing tricks behind his back,

04:15.120 --> 04:17.779
would he keep the child
and get rid of the mother?

04:36.390 --> 04:37.000
No.

04:39.120 --> 04:41.190
He saw that the Master gave me status

04:41.950 --> 04:43.880
and privileges of doing business,

04:44.950 --> 04:46.159
so he's afraid that the child in my belly

04:46.159 --> 04:47.420
will be a threat to him.

04:48.310 --> 04:48.680
Yes.

04:49.830 --> 04:50.690
That must be it.

04:53.880 --> 04:56.409
Everyone wants to see me
make a fool of myself.

04:58.680 --> 05:00.950
But I will still steal all the spotlight.

05:06.240 --> 05:08.070
Master.

05:09.330 --> 05:11.750
The photo session took too long.

05:11.770 --> 05:13.400
My legs are sore.

05:13.830 --> 05:14.830
Serves you right.

05:15.160 --> 05:16.560
No one forced you to do it.

05:16.740 --> 05:18.240
You said you wanted to learn

05:18.240 --> 05:19.120
to do business.

05:20.450 --> 05:21.450
Didn't I do it

05:21.480 --> 05:22.680
to share your burden?

05:23.000 --> 05:23.920
Besides,

05:24.270 --> 05:25.510
when our baby is born,

05:26.000 --> 05:26.720
he will say,

05:26.980 --> 05:28.160
"Mommy is pretty

05:28.160 --> 05:29.720
but incapable of doing anything else."

05:29.720 --> 05:31.050
Who will lose face then?

05:34.120 --> 05:34.720
Very well.

05:34.720 --> 05:36.040
Since you like attending

05:36.040 --> 05:37.270
these events so much,

05:37.870 --> 05:38.470
there just

05:38.870 --> 05:40.750
happens to be a banquet
at the Jockey Club.

05:40.750 --> 05:41.560
I don't want to go.

05:41.560 --> 05:42.560
You go in my place.

05:43.510 --> 05:45.240
It won't be too tiring, I think.

05:45.770 --> 05:46.650
I knew you

05:46.680 --> 05:48.140
treat me the best, Master.

05:54.170 --> 05:57.520
[Shengcheng Oriental Green Golf Club
Tee-off Ceremony]

05:54.270 --> 05:54.930
Am I pretty?

05:56.400 --> 05:58.060
The one beside me is prettier.

06:00.390 --> 06:02.120
Tell me whatever you want to eat.

06:02.120 --> 06:03.850
I'll make it and bring it to you.

06:04.430 --> 06:04.920
Okay.

06:05.640 --> 06:07.650
But I think the soup you make is

06:07.680 --> 06:08.290
so delicious.

06:08.290 --> 06:09.560
I've improved, right?

06:09.630 --> 06:10.270
Yes.

06:12.040 --> 06:12.510
Mom?

06:13.000 --> 06:14.330
Welcome back, Xiaolan.

06:14.430 --> 06:15.600
I made some buns

06:15.680 --> 06:17.410
and brought them for Granny Yu.

06:19.190 --> 06:19.800
Granny Yu.

06:20.590 --> 06:22.390
I'm going to Kong Island tomorrow.

06:22.390 --> 06:24.050
Do you want me to send anything

06:24.360 --> 06:25.310
or any messages?

06:26.630 --> 06:28.270
I have nothing to say.

06:29.560 --> 06:31.020
Those who want to come back

06:31.310 --> 06:32.840
will come back on their own.

06:35.390 --> 06:36.560
I won't see you out.

06:37.040 --> 06:39.100
Go ahead and chat with your daughter.

06:39.159 --> 06:39.530
Okay.

06:40.270 --> 06:41.610
Rest early then.

06:41.640 --> 06:42.120
Okay.

08:09.300 --> 08:09.940
Granny Yu.

08:12.900 --> 08:13.430
Morning.

08:19.790 --> 08:21.030
Give this to him.

08:24.890 --> 08:27.420
There's nothing else I want to say.

08:29.800 --> 08:30.190
Okay.

08:31.640 --> 08:32.570
I'm leaving now.

08:32.600 --> 08:32.929
Okay.

08:35.789 --> 08:36.360
Xiaolan.

08:38.890 --> 08:40.010
Take care of yourself

08:40.010 --> 08:41.539
when you reach Kong Island.

08:45.000 --> 08:45.460
I'm off.

08:46.030 --> 08:46.480
Yes.

09:03.200 --> 09:06.570
[Kong Island]

09:31.920 --> 09:33.940
[The 6th International Youth
Architectural Design Festival]

09:37.890 --> 09:38.600
She's left?

09:39.890 --> 09:40.840
Ms. Xia came to Kong Island

09:40.840 --> 09:41.640
for business.

09:42.050 --> 09:43.380
She couldn't stay long.

09:43.540 --> 09:45.360
She asked me to give this to you.

09:54.110 --> 09:55.910
Did she leave any other message?

09:56.870 --> 09:57.320
No.

10:00.840 --> 10:01.640
You may leave.

10:12.030 --> 10:12.830
In the future,

10:13.300 --> 10:14.360
who else will remember

10:14.360 --> 10:17.020
that Xu Zhongyi was born
in the Year of the Tiger?

10:21.060 --> 10:23.260
I've come to realize

10:23.370 --> 10:24.840
that in the past seven years,

10:24.840 --> 10:27.200
we've had many oriental faces

10:27.550 --> 10:31.080
and elements in this competition.

10:31.510 --> 10:35.120
And this, for the architectural sector, is

10:35.480 --> 10:37.870
very, very good.

10:42.390 --> 10:43.030
Lady!

10:45.840 --> 10:48.170
Now you want me to strike
the opening gong?

10:50.360 --> 10:50.840
Lady,

10:51.150 --> 10:52.360
if you wish to leave,

10:52.430 --> 10:53.440
please take this passage

10:53.440 --> 10:55.300
to the parking lot to get your car.

10:55.630 --> 10:57.790
Who cares about striking that crappy gong?

10:57.790 --> 10:58.870
Disrespecting me

10:59.440 --> 11:01.370
means disrespecting Chairman Du.

11:02.830 --> 11:04.090
Where is the restroom?

11:08.360 --> 11:12.920
We hope that this will bring closer
the East and the West

11:13.250 --> 11:14.650
together in the future.

11:14.910 --> 11:16.090
Thank you, Professor McCarthy,

11:16.090 --> 11:17.620
for your wonderful speech.

11:21.000 --> 11:22.750
A dancing girl is just a dancing girl.

11:22.750 --> 11:24.410
She'll never be presentable.

11:24.590 --> 11:25.920
This is the Jockey Club.

11:26.240 --> 11:28.390
Look at how much skin she's showing.

11:29.000 --> 11:30.740
Mr. Du didn't teach her any manners.

11:30.740 --> 11:33.500
She's just embarrassing
the Du family out there.

11:34.590 --> 11:37.190
Mr. Du is known for his wild ways.

11:37.450 --> 11:40.300
He wouldn't actually
fall for a dancing girl.

11:41.680 --> 11:44.920
Of course he wouldn't bother
teaching her etiquette.

11:45.550 --> 11:47.410
It's only because she's

11:47.440 --> 11:49.010
pregnant.

11:49.600 --> 11:51.200
If she's pregnant, she should stay home

11:51.200 --> 11:52.440
and rest for the baby.

11:52.760 --> 11:54.030
Did you see the look on her face

11:54.030 --> 11:55.150
when the gong was struck?

11:55.150 --> 11:57.670
She actually thought
she could go on stage and strike it.

11:57.670 --> 11:58.750
What a joke.

11:59.120 --> 12:00.910
If it weren't for Mr. Du's fame,

12:01.030 --> 12:02.670
she wouldn't even have a seat.

12:02.670 --> 12:03.700
Honestly.

12:11.480 --> 12:12.150
Mrs. Chen, Mrs. Li,

12:12.150 --> 12:13.150
don't rush off.

12:14.270 --> 12:16.530
Weren't you enjoying chatting just now?

12:16.930 --> 12:17.880
I just wondered

12:17.910 --> 12:19.310
how capable you two were.

12:19.950 --> 12:22.210
But aren't you just relying
on your husbands' reputation

12:22.210 --> 12:22.910
to be in the same venue

12:22.910 --> 12:24.040
with a dancing girl?

12:25.360 --> 12:26.070
Besides,

12:26.910 --> 12:28.410
what's wrong with dancing girls?

12:28.410 --> 12:29.450
Your husbands

12:29.480 --> 12:30.440
sent you away,

12:31.040 --> 12:31.840
but right now,

12:32.170 --> 12:33.410
they could be

12:33.440 --> 12:35.040
in some dancing girls' beds.

12:35.550 --> 12:37.320
With such stiff bones,

12:38.200 --> 12:39.260
can you even dance?

12:42.000 --> 12:43.600
The second prize goes

12:43.660 --> 12:44.780
to Xinghe Theater,

12:45.790 --> 12:46.600
designed

12:46.630 --> 12:48.030
by Xia Xiaolan

12:48.320 --> 12:49.670
from Qi Hang Design Studio.

12:49.670 --> 12:52.200
Let's give a round of applause
to welcome her.

13:03.840 --> 13:05.720
Congratulations. Well-done.

13:06.070 --> 13:07.070
See you next year.

13:07.100 --> 13:07.700
Thank you.

13:26.310 --> 13:27.570
Let me help you wash it.

13:28.720 --> 13:29.210
Come on.

13:39.360 --> 13:39.870
Good.

13:45.070 --> 13:45.980
Xia Xiaolan, you...

13:45.980 --> 13:47.380
You splashed water on me.

13:48.240 --> 13:48.910
Let me do it.

13:55.270 --> 13:56.270
Comrade Xiaolan.

13:56.610 --> 13:57.430
Let's take a break.

13:57.430 --> 13:58.960
I'll pour you a cup of water.

14:05.200 --> 14:05.930
Here you are.

14:07.000 --> 14:07.600
Thank you.

14:17.510 --> 14:18.170
Be careful.

14:20.550 --> 14:21.610
The sun is blazing.

14:22.150 --> 14:23.280
It's scorching hot.

14:23.600 --> 14:24.730
Isn't this Xiaolan?

14:25.150 --> 14:26.200
You wrote this.

14:26.260 --> 14:26.960
What is this?

14:26.960 --> 14:27.720
You like me.

14:28.510 --> 14:29.240
Give it to me!

14:29.320 --> 14:29.720
What's wrong?

14:29.720 --> 14:30.290
How shameless.

14:30.290 --> 14:31.150
Shame on you.

14:31.510 --> 14:32.750
Let go of me! Go away!

14:33.890 --> 14:35.130
You said you like me.

14:36.080 --> 14:36.960
Let go of me!

14:36.980 --> 14:38.150
So shameless.

14:42.550 --> 14:43.000
What?

14:43.510 --> 14:44.960
So many people are watching.

14:44.960 --> 14:46.220
And you won't admit it?

14:46.630 --> 14:47.870
You said you like me!

14:47.930 --> 14:50.130
You asked me out to meet you by the river!

14:52.890 --> 14:54.620
Wang Jianhua? Someone like him

14:54.910 --> 14:56.790
would throw himself at me

14:57.050 --> 14:58.910
without me even lifting a finger.

15:00.150 --> 15:00.840
Xia Ziyu,

15:01.480 --> 15:03.630
maybe you should take a good look
in the mirror

15:03.630 --> 15:04.550
and see

15:04.790 --> 15:06.190
how incompetent you are.

15:12.320 --> 15:13.660
Darn northern girl,

15:13.690 --> 15:15.020
cheating me of my money!

15:18.670 --> 15:19.670
Do you want to die?

15:33.870 --> 15:34.960
Xia Xiaolan.

15:36.580 --> 15:37.980
Why can't I get rid of you?

15:39.550 --> 15:41.550
Why are you always going against me?

15:42.360 --> 15:44.670
All my pain comes from you.

15:45.990 --> 15:47.700
Everyone else can live well,

15:49.000 --> 15:50.160
but not you.

15:52.640 --> 15:53.200
Lady!

15:53.220 --> 15:54.680
Do you have an invitation?

15:54.800 --> 15:56.920
You can't enter without an invitation.

15:56.920 --> 15:58.160
Are you blind?

15:58.840 --> 15:59.760
I'm Ms. Vivi

15:59.790 --> 16:01.050
from Chengrong Group.

16:01.080 --> 16:02.610
Do I even need an invitation

16:02.750 --> 16:04.350
to get into a place like this?

16:04.550 --> 16:05.510
Friends from the media,

16:05.510 --> 16:06.710
you may come forward.

16:31.550 --> 16:32.100
What's happening?

16:32.100 --> 16:33.030
She's bleeding.

16:35.390 --> 16:37.740
Should we call an ambulance for her?

16:38.370 --> 16:40.230
Mr. Du, please come here quickly!

16:40.550 --> 16:41.430
I don't know.

16:43.440 --> 16:44.490
Call an ambulance for me.

16:44.490 --> 16:45.730
Please call an ambulance for me.

16:45.730 --> 16:47.590
Someone call an ambulance for me.

17:28.190 --> 17:29.310
Is m-my child

17:29.330 --> 17:30.440
gone?

17:33.110 --> 17:34.040
It's in the past.

17:34.330 --> 17:35.860
Focus on recovering first.

17:38.240 --> 17:38.680
No.

17:39.360 --> 17:40.750
This was not an accident.

17:40.750 --> 17:43.350
It was Xia Xiaolan. It was Xia Xiaolan.

17:44.830 --> 17:45.510
Listen,

17:45.550 --> 17:47.150
don't let your mind run wild.

17:47.200 --> 17:49.240
Just focus on getting better now.

17:53.590 --> 17:54.400
Rest well.

18:05.260 --> 18:07.390
The Young Master has a message for you.

18:07.920 --> 18:09.700
It's actually good that the child is gone.

18:09.700 --> 18:11.060
You can use a clean identity

18:11.060 --> 18:12.580
to carry out his plan.

18:13.080 --> 18:14.990
The choice is yours to make.

18:20.440 --> 18:21.640
Tell the Young Master

18:21.960 --> 18:23.490
that I accept his proposal.

18:23.960 --> 18:25.360
I'll do whatever he says.

18:25.840 --> 18:26.270
Good.

18:27.200 --> 18:28.600
I'll go back and tell him.

18:31.960 --> 18:32.720
Xia Xiaolan,

18:33.440 --> 18:35.110
I will climb up the social ladder.

18:35.110 --> 18:36.910
I will obtain wealth and status.

18:37.510 --> 18:38.710
When that time comes,

18:39.070 --> 18:40.200
I will make you taste

18:40.260 --> 18:42.190
what it's like to lose everything.

19:09.880 --> 19:11.030
Master.

19:17.830 --> 19:19.160
What are you doing here?

19:19.160 --> 19:20.420
Is this how you usually

19:20.500 --> 19:21.830
win the Old Man's favor?

19:25.760 --> 19:27.170
He really has gotten old.

19:28.520 --> 19:29.810
Such cheap tricks,

19:30.250 --> 19:31.710
and he still fell for them.

19:33.200 --> 19:34.930
But they don't work now, right?

19:35.550 --> 19:36.310
He probably

19:37.070 --> 19:38.670
won't come to meet you again.

19:40.550 --> 19:42.150
Isn't that all thanks to you?

19:42.640 --> 19:43.240
What?

19:44.920 --> 19:46.780
Are you dissatisfied with me now?

19:47.160 --> 19:49.290
The Old Man doesn't come to me anymore,

19:49.750 --> 19:51.150
so you think I'm useless?

19:53.680 --> 19:55.540
Let me correct a mistake of yours.

19:56.440 --> 19:58.970
I've thought you were useless
for a long time.

19:59.350 --> 20:00.790
But if you were capable

20:00.900 --> 20:02.560
of winning the Old Man's favor

20:02.790 --> 20:03.760
and securing a place

20:03.760 --> 20:04.890
in our Du family,

20:05.440 --> 20:07.770
I wouldn't stand in the way
of your riches.

20:10.160 --> 20:11.110
But what a pity.

20:13.110 --> 20:14.440
You were too impatient.

20:15.310 --> 20:16.910
You wasted the bright future

20:17.030 --> 20:17.920
you once had.

20:21.750 --> 20:22.680
What do you mean?

20:23.860 --> 20:24.590
You had already won

20:24.590 --> 20:25.680
the Old Man's favor

20:26.310 --> 20:28.170
and were pregnant with his child.

20:28.550 --> 20:29.220
If you'd just prepared well

20:29.220 --> 20:30.270
to be a mistress in the Du family,

20:30.270 --> 20:31.720
wouldn't that have been enough?

20:31.720 --> 20:34.970
But you insisted on going
and picking a fight with Xia Xiaolan.

20:34.970 --> 20:36.110
If you hadn't tried to do that,

20:36.110 --> 20:36.720
maybe

20:38.160 --> 20:38.790
the Old Man

20:39.640 --> 20:41.700
would have rewarded you with a house.

20:46.680 --> 20:47.640
Du Zhaohui,

20:48.640 --> 20:51.570
you're still obsessed
with Xia Xiaolan, aren't you?

20:53.240 --> 20:54.170
What do you mean?

20:55.150 --> 20:56.640
You want to help clear Xia Xiaolan
of suspicion,

20:56.640 --> 20:57.110
right?

20:57.840 --> 20:58.680
You want to convince me

20:58.680 --> 20:59.900
that losing the baby in my belly

20:59.900 --> 21:01.240
had nothing to do with her,

21:01.240 --> 21:03.440
and that it was just an accident, right?

21:03.960 --> 21:05.620
Do you think I'd believe that?

21:06.510 --> 21:07.440
Out of nowhere,

21:08.030 --> 21:09.370
she just happened to show up
on the same day as me,

21:09.370 --> 21:10.930
at the same hotel,

21:10.960 --> 21:11.960
on the same floor?

21:15.830 --> 21:16.550
Xia Ziyu,

21:17.720 --> 21:18.590
don't go nuts.

21:20.550 --> 21:21.950
Sometimes I really doubt

21:22.070 --> 21:22.850
if you and Xia Xiaolan

21:22.850 --> 21:24.330
really grew up together

21:24.830 --> 21:25.490
as cousins.

21:27.200 --> 21:27.860
Xia Xiaolan

21:28.400 --> 21:28.960
doesn't even

21:28.960 --> 21:30.130
care about you at all.

21:30.130 --> 21:31.060
She would never,

21:31.880 --> 21:32.590
nor does she need

21:32.590 --> 21:33.790
to use such despicable means

21:33.790 --> 21:34.720
to deal with you.

21:37.820 --> 21:39.000
You make it sound like she's

21:39.000 --> 21:40.730
some sort of innocent goddess.

21:41.680 --> 21:43.010
What makes her so noble?

21:43.940 --> 21:44.870
Doesn't she also

21:44.880 --> 21:45.830
rely on men?

21:49.000 --> 21:49.790
It's just

21:50.750 --> 21:53.280
that she doesn't rely on you,
Young Master Du.

21:55.180 --> 21:57.380
No matter how hard you try to please her,

21:58.720 --> 22:01.510
she still won't spare you a glance.

22:07.300 --> 22:08.270
I'm not sure if she'll

22:08.270 --> 22:09.270
spare me a glance.

22:10.030 --> 22:10.960
But I'm sure

22:11.720 --> 22:12.510
the Old Man

22:14.000 --> 22:15.800
won't spare you a single glance.

22:47.550 --> 22:48.480
This court finds

22:48.640 --> 22:50.200
the defendants, Liu Tianquan,

22:50.200 --> 22:52.920
Xiao Jianyong, Zhang Donglai,
and Zhang Sanjun,

22:52.920 --> 22:55.240
guilty of intentional homicide
and smuggling.

22:55.240 --> 22:57.510
In accordance with the laws
of the People's Republic of China,

22:57.510 --> 22:58.970
the verdict is as follows.

22:59.640 --> 23:01.110
Defendant Liu Tianquan

23:01.240 --> 23:03.200
committed the crime
of intentional homicide

23:03.200 --> 23:04.750
by cruel means,

23:05.110 --> 23:06.600
causing extremely serious consequences,

23:06.600 --> 23:07.800
posing

23:07.830 --> 23:09.030
great threats to society.

23:09.030 --> 23:10.960
He is hereby sentenced to death

23:11.110 --> 23:12.750
and deprived of political rights for life

23:12.750 --> 23:13.750
as a punishment.

23:14.960 --> 23:16.360
Defendant Liu Tianquan,

23:16.590 --> 23:18.110
in his smuggling activities,

23:18.110 --> 23:20.310
violated national customs regulations.

23:20.310 --> 23:21.510
The circumstances are serious,

23:21.510 --> 23:22.750
causing major losses

23:22.770 --> 23:24.630
to national economic interests.

23:24.750 --> 23:26.590
In accordance with relevant laws,

23:26.590 --> 23:28.640
he is sentenced to 15 years in prison

23:29.110 --> 23:30.030
and fined

23:30.270 --> 23:32.150
5.5 million RMB

23:32.510 --> 23:34.770
to demonstrate the authority of the law.

23:34.850 --> 23:37.780
[Shengcheng People's Court]

23:36.270 --> 23:38.070
Xia Ziyu has fallen out of favor?

23:38.370 --> 23:39.370
The Old Man

23:39.400 --> 23:41.070
got tired of her a long time ago.

23:41.070 --> 23:43.330
He did it
for the sake of the child before.

23:43.440 --> 23:45.100
But now that the child is gone,

23:45.810 --> 23:46.640
the Old Man hasn't

23:46.640 --> 23:48.300
gone to see her for a long time.

23:49.200 --> 23:49.880
However,

23:50.160 --> 23:51.590
because of what happened to Liu Tianquan,

23:51.590 --> 23:52.240
he seems to be treating

23:52.240 --> 23:54.110
Liu Keying a bit better recently.

23:55.680 --> 23:56.940
I really didn't expect

23:57.000 --> 23:58.030
that the Old Man

23:58.520 --> 23:59.480
would actually hand over

23:59.480 --> 24:00.280
Liu Tianquan.

24:00.730 --> 24:02.220
To clean up its image, Chengrong Group

24:02.220 --> 24:03.090
severed a limb.

24:03.550 --> 24:05.030
The Du family has officially

24:05.030 --> 24:06.510
cut ties with shady businesses

24:06.510 --> 24:08.310
and turned to legal operations.

24:08.790 --> 24:09.450
Du Zhaohui,

24:09.790 --> 24:11.190
you chose the right path.

24:11.450 --> 24:12.440
It's a pity the Old Man is

24:12.440 --> 24:13.960
not completely heartless.

24:13.960 --> 24:15.720
He only handed over Liu Tianquan.

24:15.720 --> 24:16.520
You know what?

24:16.560 --> 24:17.410
The smuggling ring was

24:17.410 --> 24:18.080
in the hands

24:18.110 --> 24:19.240
of Brat Ji all along.

24:19.400 --> 24:20.110
Two days ago,

24:20.110 --> 24:21.640
he warned Brat Ji

24:22.200 --> 24:24.310
to cut off all the smuggling businesses.

24:24.310 --> 24:25.510
Usually, that guy

24:25.840 --> 24:27.590
dresses up like some decent gentleman.

24:27.590 --> 24:28.350
I didn't expect

24:28.350 --> 24:30.160
that he'd want to be a gangster
more than I do.

24:30.160 --> 24:31.320
His reaction seemed

24:31.350 --> 24:32.030
even more nervous

24:32.030 --> 24:32.830
than when he lost

24:32.830 --> 24:34.030
that 5% of the shares.

24:36.580 --> 24:37.230
Listen,

24:37.790 --> 24:39.190
you'd better be careful.

24:39.270 --> 24:40.240
Xia Ziyu

24:40.510 --> 24:41.680
hates your guts.

24:42.310 --> 24:43.400
Thanks for the heads-up.

24:43.400 --> 24:44.600
I'll take it to heart.

24:44.970 --> 24:45.800
I think

24:45.830 --> 24:47.690
you should also watch out for Du Zhaoji.

24:47.690 --> 24:48.560
He's just

24:48.590 --> 24:50.320
as small-minded as Xia Ziyu is.

24:50.510 --> 24:51.310
You're so smug now.

24:51.310 --> 24:53.440
Be careful, he might plot against you.

24:54.120 --> 24:54.830
Is there anything else?

24:54.830 --> 24:56.090
If not, I'm hanging up.

24:56.240 --> 24:56.700
Hold on.

24:58.350 --> 24:59.750
Are you worried about me?

25:00.960 --> 25:01.640
So,

25:01.890 --> 25:02.960
you've forgiven me for hiding things

25:02.960 --> 25:03.590
from you?

25:04.440 --> 25:06.590
I haven't been to Shengcheng
for a long time.

25:06.590 --> 25:08.590
How about we grab a coffee tomorrow?

25:08.790 --> 25:09.590
No.

25:09.960 --> 25:11.890
Zhou Cheng and I are going back
to Anqing tomorrow.

25:11.890 --> 25:13.350
We'll handle the scholarship first,

25:13.350 --> 25:14.830
then return to Jingcheng
for our marriage certificate.

25:14.830 --> 25:16.200
As for coffee, let's talk about it

25:16.200 --> 25:16.800
next time.

25:19.320 --> 25:25.240
♪ Why do you always say that line? ♪

25:25.260 --> 25:30.890
♪ Why am I unwilling to give up? ♪

25:30.160 --> 25:31.790
Call the department store manager over
for me.

25:30.910 --> 25:37.140
♪ I realize that love
shouldn't mean losing it all ♪

25:32.510 --> 25:34.310
I want to pick

25:34.830 --> 25:36.290
a wedding gift for Ms. Xia.

25:36.570 --> 25:37.510
No problem, Young Master.

25:37.430 --> 25:42.540
♪ Yet somehow, I can't help but like you ♪

25:37.830 --> 25:38.890
I'll go get him now.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.240
How did it go?

25:46.110 --> 25:47.160
The verdict is out.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.160
We won the lawsuit

25:48.350 --> 25:50.550
and got the appropriate compensation.

25:50.790 --> 25:52.350
Mr. Wu, Mr. Zhou,

25:52.830 --> 25:53.510
thank you.

25:53.950 --> 25:55.480
Thanks to you not giving up,

25:55.560 --> 25:56.440
we finally got justice

25:56.440 --> 25:57.540
for Shi Kai.

25:58.350 --> 25:58.940
Thank you both.

25:58.940 --> 26:00.740
It's nothing. Don't mention it.

26:03.640 --> 26:04.170
Alright,

26:04.400 --> 26:05.240
you guys go ahead.

26:05.240 --> 26:06.880
I'll send Ms. Wei back to the hotel.

26:06.880 --> 26:08.210
When are you going back?

26:08.680 --> 26:09.280
Tomorrow.

26:09.830 --> 26:10.590
We'll stay for a couple of days

26:10.590 --> 26:11.640
and then come back.

26:11.640 --> 26:12.840
It won't affect work.

26:13.070 --> 26:13.530
Come on.

26:13.750 --> 26:14.510
It's rare for you to go back.

26:14.510 --> 26:15.920
Why not stay a few more days?

26:15.920 --> 26:17.980
Consider it my gift to your marriage.

26:18.110 --> 26:18.710
We're off.

26:21.000 --> 26:21.930
Thank you.

26:24.440 --> 26:25.440
Drive carefully.

26:26.720 --> 26:27.650
We'll get going.

26:32.200 --> 26:33.000
Drive safely.

26:34.400 --> 26:34.930
Let's go.

26:49.240 --> 26:51.170
Congratulations, Attorney Zhou.

26:52.640 --> 26:53.270
Thank you,

26:53.880 --> 26:54.510
Mrs. Zhou.

27:18.350 --> 27:19.410
What are you doing?

27:20.550 --> 27:21.800
-Mr. Tang.
-Mr. Tang.

27:22.780 --> 27:23.550
You're already here.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.350
Hurry inside.

27:25.550 --> 27:25.960
Okay.

27:35.880 --> 27:37.140
Take the fruit basket.

27:41.590 --> 27:42.190
After you.

27:45.510 --> 27:46.040
Mrs. Liu.

27:46.160 --> 27:47.890
-Mom.
-You came back together?

27:48.480 --> 27:49.240
I happened

27:49.270 --> 27:50.640
to run into them at the door.

27:50.640 --> 27:50.960
Mom,

27:50.990 --> 27:53.050
Zhou Cheng bought some soda and wine.

27:54.000 --> 27:55.600
You put the soda on the table?

27:55.790 --> 27:57.320
It needs to go to the fridge.

27:57.480 --> 27:58.740
Show some initiative.

27:59.270 --> 27:59.640
Okay.

28:00.400 --> 28:00.920
Well,

28:01.310 --> 28:01.750
Tang,

28:02.130 --> 28:03.350
go to the kitchen and help me check

28:03.350 --> 28:04.510
the heat of my soup.

28:04.860 --> 28:05.960
I still can't master the cooking

28:05.960 --> 28:07.070
of this Cantonese soup.

28:07.070 --> 28:08.550
I'm afraid it won't taste good.

28:08.550 --> 28:10.210
Any soup you make tastes good.

28:11.120 --> 28:12.380
So you didn't buy wine?

28:13.530 --> 28:14.400
Why are you still standing there?

28:14.400 --> 28:15.640
Hurry into the kitchen.

28:15.640 --> 28:16.070
Okay.

28:16.270 --> 28:16.870
I'm going.

28:17.050 --> 28:17.640
Go ahead.

28:22.030 --> 28:23.830
What's going on with those two?

28:24.590 --> 28:26.650
Nothing.

28:26.680 --> 28:28.000
We just stayed in the car for a while

28:28.000 --> 28:28.530
just now.

28:29.160 --> 28:30.400
What were you and Zhou Cheng

28:30.400 --> 28:31.330
doing in the car?

28:33.790 --> 28:34.590
Just...

28:46.720 --> 28:47.720
Gently.

28:48.420 --> 28:48.830
Okay.

28:49.920 --> 28:50.680
Harder.

28:51.590 --> 28:52.590
Keep kneading it.

28:53.430 --> 28:55.360
Didn't you master it well just now?

29:07.000 --> 29:07.730
Why so rough?

29:08.920 --> 29:10.120
I failed to go gently.

29:10.440 --> 29:11.700
You're still so young.

29:12.830 --> 29:14.890
Sometimes you can't control it well.

29:17.240 --> 29:17.770
Xiaolan.

29:18.200 --> 29:19.150
Zhou is not bad.

29:19.170 --> 29:20.960
He is learning to knead dough
with Mr. Tang.

29:20.960 --> 29:21.960
He knows the right force,

29:21.960 --> 29:23.030
handling it with ease.

29:23.030 --> 29:23.790
Really?

29:24.000 --> 29:25.000
He's that gifted?

29:25.920 --> 29:27.480
I could smell Fen's soup

29:27.480 --> 29:29.160
from miles away.

29:29.360 --> 29:30.450
We're all late.

29:30.480 --> 29:31.310
Sorry for that. Sorry.

29:31.310 --> 29:32.400
You bought so many things.

29:32.400 --> 29:32.960
This is great.

29:32.960 --> 29:34.310
Hello, Auntie, Xiaolan.

29:34.310 --> 29:35.570
Hello. Hello, Taotao.

29:35.790 --> 29:37.560
If it smells good, eat more tonight.

29:37.560 --> 29:38.480
Mr. Tang and Zhou Cheng are teaching

29:38.480 --> 29:41.610
and learning how to knead dough
in the kitchen upstairs.

29:41.790 --> 29:43.160
He's working in the kitchen?

29:43.160 --> 29:43.600
Right.

29:44.590 --> 29:45.030
Good.

29:46.000 --> 29:47.720
He just needs to learn

29:47.780 --> 29:49.310
the kitchen work properly.

29:49.480 --> 29:50.540
I'll go take a look.

29:51.020 --> 29:52.420
What kind of talk is that?

29:52.830 --> 29:53.490
Ignore him.

29:54.240 --> 29:55.200
I've got your back.

29:55.200 --> 29:55.600
Right?

29:55.790 --> 29:56.850
We all support you.

29:57.240 --> 29:59.360
What's going on today?

29:59.430 --> 30:00.510
Why are Uncle and Mr. Tang

30:00.510 --> 30:01.750
so fond of Zhou Cheng?

30:02.240 --> 30:03.480
What's going on here?

30:03.830 --> 30:05.350
What else could it be?

30:05.720 --> 30:08.250
A father-in-law nitpicking his son-in-law.

30:08.870 --> 30:09.480
Granny Yu.

30:09.510 --> 30:11.030
Quickly, say hello to Granny Yu.

30:11.030 --> 30:12.030
Hello, Granny Yu.

30:12.160 --> 30:12.790
Hello.

30:19.200 --> 30:19.790
Cheng,

30:20.070 --> 30:22.130
did you make the dough for these buns?

30:22.720 --> 30:23.070
Yes.

30:23.920 --> 30:25.580
I learned from Mr. Tang today.

30:26.400 --> 30:26.930
The buns.

30:28.000 --> 30:29.590
You'll get
your marriage certificate tomorrow.

30:29.590 --> 30:30.830
Why are you in such a rush?

30:30.830 --> 30:32.430
Can't the wedding wait a bit?

30:34.070 --> 30:35.070
Of course I'm in a rush.

30:35.070 --> 30:36.210
If I don't hurry,

30:36.340 --> 30:37.800
what if Xiaolan runs away?

30:38.880 --> 30:39.960
As outstanding as she is,

30:39.960 --> 30:41.510
I'm not the only one who likes her.

30:41.510 --> 30:42.970
Others will like her, too.

30:43.680 --> 30:44.740
But marriage isn't

30:44.960 --> 30:46.310
about tying her down.

30:46.920 --> 30:47.590
She

30:48.030 --> 30:48.790
and her heart

30:49.350 --> 30:50.410
will still be free.

30:51.550 --> 30:52.960
If I don't do well,

30:53.510 --> 30:54.920
she can still leave me.

30:55.830 --> 30:56.400
But I won't

30:56.400 --> 30:57.480
let that happen.

30:58.000 --> 30:59.460
Although life in the future

30:59.460 --> 31:00.920
may not be smooth sailing,

31:01.200 --> 31:02.730
because we love each other,

31:02.940 --> 31:04.470
we're willing to join hands

31:04.480 --> 31:06.140
to enter the next stage of life

31:06.480 --> 31:07.480
and to face together

31:07.480 --> 31:08.790
various challenges

31:08.920 --> 31:10.120
the future may bring.

31:11.790 --> 31:13.280
Well said!

31:13.310 --> 31:15.240
Let's give him a round of applause!

31:16.070 --> 31:16.550
Dad,

31:17.200 --> 31:17.790
Mr. Tang,

31:18.160 --> 31:19.210
are you satisfied

31:19.240 --> 31:20.640
with Zhou Cheng's reply?

31:21.640 --> 31:22.820
What do you mean by "satisfied"...

31:22.820 --> 31:23.950
You little traitor!

31:24.070 --> 31:24.830
Come on.

31:24.920 --> 31:25.360
Cheers.

31:25.360 --> 31:26.000
Cheers.

31:26.070 --> 31:27.130
Congratulations.

31:34.510 --> 31:35.850
Looking back now,

31:35.880 --> 31:36.640
it feels like

31:37.030 --> 31:38.510
it was a lifetime ago.

31:40.590 --> 31:42.110
Back then,

31:43.720 --> 31:45.780
you didn't care much about anything.

31:46.070 --> 31:47.480
But during that time,

31:48.510 --> 31:50.310
you were always so cautious

31:50.960 --> 31:51.830
and wary.

31:52.640 --> 31:54.040
Every day, it seemed like

31:54.960 --> 31:56.830
you were looking for something.

31:58.790 --> 31:59.590
So,

32:00.510 --> 32:02.480
you noticed it, too.

32:04.910 --> 32:06.150
I gave birth to you.

32:07.000 --> 32:08.160
I'm your mom.

32:09.200 --> 32:10.600
How could I not notice it?

32:16.200 --> 32:17.240
But I thought

32:18.200 --> 32:19.270
my daughter

32:19.830 --> 32:21.560
had suffered so much injustice

32:22.310 --> 32:23.640
and been through a lot.

32:24.750 --> 32:26.210
No matter what she became,

32:27.510 --> 32:29.110
she'd always be my daughter.

32:31.550 --> 32:33.160
As long as we're together,

32:34.240 --> 32:35.500
nothing else matters.

32:42.960 --> 32:44.290
What's wrong, Xiaolan?

32:46.240 --> 32:46.830
Nothing.

32:49.270 --> 32:49.720
Mom,

32:50.550 --> 32:51.240
I love you.

32:54.920 --> 32:56.030
I love you too.

33:07.830 --> 33:09.640
I don't know if it's possible

33:10.270 --> 33:11.510
that Liu Fen realized

33:12.200 --> 33:13.000
I'm not his daughter

33:13.000 --> 33:14.330
by spotting the change.

33:15.880 --> 33:17.070
But no matter what,

33:17.510 --> 33:19.000
she gave me selfless,

33:19.160 --> 33:20.160
complete love,

33:20.960 --> 33:22.620
allowing the past Xia Xiaolan

33:22.800 --> 33:24.610
to become a braver Xia Xiaolan.

33:26.310 --> 33:27.920
She gave so much love

33:28.870 --> 33:30.870
and also received so much in return.

33:41.380 --> 33:43.000
[Anqing No. 1 High School]
[A warm welcome to alumna Xia Xiaolan]

33:44.270 --> 33:46.270
A warm welcome to Xia Xiaolan?

33:47.160 --> 33:48.160
Xia Xiaolan?

33:49.360 --> 33:49.970
Why does

33:50.000 --> 33:51.550
this name sound so familiar?

33:51.550 --> 33:52.280
Here you are.

33:52.400 --> 33:53.330
What does she do?

33:54.000 --> 33:55.920
You don't know Xia Xiaolan?

33:56.310 --> 33:57.510
She was Yunan Province's top scorer

33:57.510 --> 33:59.510
in the college entrance exam back then.

33:59.510 --> 34:01.430
She's a big boss now.

34:01.590 --> 34:03.270
She even won an architectural award.

34:03.270 --> 34:04.530
She's really amazing.

34:04.640 --> 34:06.350
My business was just average back then,

34:06.350 --> 34:07.550
but she gave me some advice,

34:07.550 --> 34:08.670
and suddenly,

34:08.800 --> 34:09.710
it took off.

34:10.710 --> 34:12.280
She's been smart since she was a kid.

34:12.280 --> 34:12.880
Last time,

34:13.070 --> 34:14.000
she donated

34:14.360 --> 34:16.110
a library to the school.

34:17.030 --> 34:18.560
This time, she's setting up

34:19.590 --> 34:20.449
a scholarship!

34:20.880 --> 34:22.400
In the future, local kids

34:22.659 --> 34:24.280
who can't afford school fees

34:24.320 --> 34:25.670
will have solutions!

34:29.550 --> 34:30.409
President Sun,

34:30.920 --> 34:31.850
look who's here.

34:36.480 --> 34:37.480
Xiaolan?

34:38.440 --> 34:39.449
Mr. Sun.

34:39.780 --> 34:41.190
Hello, hello.

34:41.360 --> 34:42.150
Long time no see.

34:42.150 --> 34:42.840
Indeed.

34:44.480 --> 34:45.440
You've changed.

34:45.960 --> 34:47.070
You've matured

34:47.440 --> 34:48.710
and become more beautiful.

34:48.710 --> 34:49.600
And you.

34:49.630 --> 34:50.400
You haven't changed a bit.

34:50.400 --> 34:51.480
You're still so young.

34:51.480 --> 34:52.550
Not at all.

34:52.710 --> 34:53.110
Look

34:53.280 --> 34:55.110
at all my gray hair.

34:55.320 --> 34:56.650
I'm retiring next year.

34:56.920 --> 34:59.000
I didn't expect I could see you back here

34:59.000 --> 35:00.860
to visit me before my retirement.

35:01.280 --> 35:02.440
I get it.

35:02.480 --> 35:03.520
Mr. Sun, you're blaming me

35:03.520 --> 35:04.670
for not coming back to visit you often.

35:04.670 --> 35:05.710
No, not at all.

35:07.450 --> 35:08.160
Who is this?

35:08.190 --> 35:09.280
This is Zhou Cheng.

35:10.030 --> 35:11.190
My fiancé.

35:11.760 --> 35:12.560
Hello, hello.

35:12.590 --> 35:13.520
Nice to meet you.

35:14.110 --> 35:15.440
What a decent young man!

35:15.770 --> 35:16.370
Thank you.

35:16.550 --> 35:17.710
Let me show you

35:18.000 --> 35:18.510
around the school

35:18.510 --> 35:19.360
to see all the changes.

35:19.360 --> 35:20.190
I'll give you a tour.

35:20.190 --> 35:20.590
Let's go.

35:20.590 --> 35:20.920
Okay.

35:21.550 --> 35:22.080
Xiaolan,

35:22.360 --> 35:24.070
our school has changed a lot.

35:24.360 --> 35:25.440
The old desks

35:25.720 --> 35:27.920
and chairs have all been replaced.

35:27.280 --> 35:30.150
[Reminisce about the youth and talk
about the lasting ties with the alma mater]

35:34.280 --> 35:35.190
Students,

35:35.920 --> 35:37.590
today, our alumna,

35:37.710 --> 35:39.070
Miss Xia Xiaolan,

35:39.150 --> 35:41.360
came back to establish a scholarship.

35:41.710 --> 35:42.440
I

35:42.890 --> 35:44.070
insisted on having her

35:44.070 --> 35:45.110
talk to you all.

35:46.110 --> 35:47.920
Over the years, Xiaolan

35:48.230 --> 35:50.550
has risen from a rural background

35:50.880 --> 35:52.320
through her own efforts,

35:52.550 --> 35:54.760
starting at our Anqing No.1 High School,

35:54.760 --> 35:55.960
moving on to Huaqing,

35:56.110 --> 35:57.240
then to Shengcheng,

35:57.450 --> 35:58.920
and finally to the front lines

35:58.920 --> 36:00.000
of socialist construction.

36:00.000 --> 36:01.720
And after achieving success,

36:01.960 --> 36:03.960
she hasn't forgotten
to give back to her alma mater.

36:03.960 --> 36:05.230
Her life experience

36:05.360 --> 36:06.600
will surely

36:06.630 --> 36:07.670
inspire you all.

36:08.360 --> 36:10.360
Let's give a round of applause

36:10.480 --> 36:12.800
to welcome Miss Xia Xiaolan.

36:23.440 --> 36:24.070
Students,

36:24.320 --> 36:25.000
hello.

36:25.360 --> 36:26.320
I am Xia Xiaolan.

36:27.670 --> 36:29.070
I used to be just like you,

36:29.670 --> 36:31.440
longing to find in a few words,

36:31.840 --> 36:33.070
in a good book,

36:33.440 --> 36:34.730
or in a speech,

36:35.000 --> 36:36.480
the secret to success.

36:37.080 --> 36:38.000
As if once I grasped

36:38.000 --> 36:38.880
this secret,

36:39.210 --> 36:40.290
I could find

36:40.320 --> 36:41.670
a shortcut to success.

36:42.800 --> 36:43.630
But sorry,

36:44.110 --> 36:44.800
I'm going

36:44.900 --> 36:46.300
to disappoint you today.

36:47.150 --> 36:48.150
Because I am still

36:48.150 --> 36:49.550
on the path of searching.

36:52.030 --> 36:53.670
Some of you might think

36:54.440 --> 36:56.840
I seem to have succeeded already.

36:57.300 --> 36:58.280
Am I just unwilling

36:58.280 --> 36:59.410
to share it with you?

37:00.840 --> 37:02.190
That is not the case.

37:02.930 --> 37:04.120
I have indeed made

37:04.150 --> 37:05.560
some brilliant achievements

37:05.560 --> 37:06.590
and gained something

37:06.590 --> 37:08.000
I once desired.

37:08.710 --> 37:10.510
But during this process,

37:10.760 --> 37:12.440
that wasn't the goal.

37:13.510 --> 37:14.710
My goal was

37:14.800 --> 37:16.070
to seek an answer.

37:17.400 --> 37:18.550
What kind of person do I

37:18.550 --> 37:19.810
really want to become,

37:20.800 --> 37:22.860
and what kind of life do I want to live?

37:24.070 --> 37:25.400
Studying in a small place

37:25.400 --> 37:26.840
like Anqing,

37:27.320 --> 37:28.590
many students are

37:28.800 --> 37:30.760
from underdeveloped rural areas.

37:31.760 --> 37:32.800
Perhaps you think

37:33.150 --> 37:34.760
that from birth,

37:35.190 --> 37:37.450
we are already many steps behind others.

37:38.030 --> 37:39.560
Then isn't pursuing dreams

37:40.070 --> 37:41.590
and life ideals

37:42.000 --> 37:43.510
just a pipe dream?

37:43.820 --> 37:45.300
Cheap and good!

37:46.000 --> 37:47.550
But I don't think so.

37:48.760 --> 37:50.940
Despite the different starting points,

37:50.940 --> 37:52.900
the roads to a dream life are all

37:53.100 --> 37:54.760
filled with twists and turns.

37:54.960 --> 37:56.550
Finding the answer to life is

37:56.550 --> 37:57.880
just like doing a test.

37:59.150 --> 38:00.030
Sometimes,

38:00.540 --> 38:02.130
you can't immediately choose

38:02.130 --> 38:03.990
the right answer with certainty.

38:04.260 --> 38:05.360
Instead, you need to eliminate

38:05.360 --> 38:06.550
many wrong options.

38:08.360 --> 38:09.440
Back in Anqing,

38:09.920 --> 38:11.650
I didn't have any grand ideals.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.030
I only wanted to escape

38:13.030 --> 38:14.630
this hard life.

38:15.550 --> 38:18.840
So, ever since
the National College Entrance Examination,

38:18.840 --> 38:19.840
I've done everything

38:19.840 --> 38:21.070
in my power

38:21.480 --> 38:23.410
to get rid of the life I didn't want.

38:25.590 --> 38:26.800
To find

38:27.020 --> 38:28.550
the final correct answer is

38:28.550 --> 38:29.280
really hard.

38:30.280 --> 38:32.710
Sometimes, you'll face difficulties.

38:33.360 --> 38:35.760
Sometimes, you'll encounter setbacks.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.340
Not just bumps in the road,

38:39.030 --> 38:40.190
but true suffering.

38:42.070 --> 38:44.800
But as long as you grit your teeth
and keep pushing

38:44.920 --> 38:46.320
just a little bit longer,

38:47.030 --> 38:48.960
these things won't matter anymore.

38:48.960 --> 38:50.710
You will surely gain more.

38:52.120 --> 38:52.850
You will find

38:52.880 --> 38:54.680
friends sharing the same goals,

38:54.800 --> 38:56.190
a more determined self,

38:56.670 --> 38:58.880
and a clearer direction in life.

38:59.720 --> 39:00.410
I hope you

39:00.440 --> 39:02.100
won't be afraid of the future.

39:02.150 --> 39:03.670
Don't let fear

39:04.030 --> 39:05.490
make you lose your dreams.

39:05.840 --> 39:07.350
Social conventions

39:07.630 --> 39:08.760
won't limit you.

39:09.440 --> 39:11.370
The only thing that can limit you is

39:11.440 --> 39:12.550
yourselves.

39:13.920 --> 39:14.630
Success is

39:15.200 --> 39:16.680
a prize found

39:16.710 --> 39:18.570
on the journey to life's answers.

39:19.000 --> 39:20.930
What's more important than that is

39:21.010 --> 39:21.880
what kind of life

39:21.880 --> 39:23.000
you want to live.

39:25.030 --> 39:25.800
Students,

39:26.760 --> 39:27.880
no matter when,

39:28.320 --> 39:29.760
I hope you believe,

39:31.000 --> 39:32.800
"The sea's vast for fish to leap,

39:32.880 --> 39:34.810
and the sky's wide for birds to fly.

39:34.880 --> 39:36.080
Thank you, everyone.

39:54.800 --> 39:56.330
Do your homework properly.

40:10.070 --> 40:12.870
You've made money
from that fast food restaurant.

40:13.320 --> 40:15.720
Aren't you going to get Grandma
a big house?

40:16.150 --> 40:16.840
Grandma,

40:17.400 --> 40:18.150
my parents and I

40:18.150 --> 40:19.890
usually live at the restaurant.

40:19.890 --> 40:21.160
There are 3 rooms here!

40:21.190 --> 40:23.510
It's usually just you
and the two of them living here.

40:23.510 --> 40:24.760
It's much more spacious
compared to when Uncle Dajun

40:24.760 --> 40:26.000
and his family were here!

40:26.000 --> 40:27.730
There's no need for a big house.

40:28.670 --> 40:30.550
You call this spacious?

40:32.040 --> 40:33.070
Compared to that courtyard

40:33.070 --> 40:34.110
in our rural hometown,

40:34.110 --> 40:34.670
is it big?

40:36.710 --> 40:38.670
I didn't come here to suffer.

40:40.930 --> 40:42.330
If you're really missing

40:42.360 --> 40:44.290
the big courtyard in our hometown,

40:44.390 --> 40:45.590
I'll send you back tomorrow.

40:45.590 --> 40:46.590
How dare you?

40:47.400 --> 40:48.030
I...

40:48.630 --> 40:50.710
You... I... I...

40:51.050 --> 40:52.890
I'm not going back to serve

40:52.920 --> 40:54.190
that little vixen.

40:55.710 --> 40:56.170
Enough.

40:56.760 --> 40:57.290
Grandma.

40:57.840 --> 41:00.100
You should tidy up a bit when you're free.

41:00.190 --> 41:01.400
Then I'll come back less often,

41:01.400 --> 41:02.530
so I won't annoy you.

41:03.110 --> 41:05.480
I'm too old to work now.

41:06.520 --> 41:07.280
I'm leaving.

41:14.880 --> 41:15.760
Uncle Dajun?

41:17.230 --> 41:18.190
Why are you back?

41:18.880 --> 41:19.740
Just you alone?

41:19.920 --> 41:21.000
Dajun.

41:21.320 --> 41:22.360
Is that Dajun?

41:22.840 --> 41:24.030
You're back.

41:24.410 --> 41:25.630
Have you made a fortune?

41:25.630 --> 41:26.880
Are you taking me to live

41:26.880 --> 41:28.030
in a big house?

41:39.030 --> 41:41.500
How did you end up like this?

41:47.910 --> 41:48.570
Who are you?

41:49.150 --> 41:49.810
Who are you?

41:50.630 --> 41:51.320
Who is he?

41:51.630 --> 41:52.630
None of your business.

41:52.630 --> 41:53.890
N-None of my business?

41:53.900 --> 41:54.760
Seriously?

41:55.800 --> 41:56.840
You dare hit her?

41:57.030 --> 41:58.320
You good-for-nothing!

41:58.320 --> 41:59.180
You're a loser,

41:59.280 --> 42:00.590
yet you dare beat your wife?

42:00.590 --> 42:01.320
How dare you?

42:01.440 --> 42:02.320
How dare you beat your wife?

42:02.320 --> 42:03.480
This is what you get for beating me!

42:03.480 --> 42:04.290
Fan Yu.

42:04.400 --> 42:05.650
Do you still want to have a family,

42:05.650 --> 42:06.320
Xia Dajun?

42:06.510 --> 42:07.420
Do you still want to have

42:07.420 --> 42:08.680
this family, Xia Da...

42:13.280 --> 42:14.190
What?

42:15.560 --> 42:17.120
You failed to keep your wife

42:17.150 --> 42:19.110
and came back all alone, huh?

42:21.630 --> 42:23.090
Where is my grandson then?

42:24.450 --> 42:25.680
I'm asking you!

42:25.710 --> 42:27.320
Where is my grandson?

42:31.000 --> 42:32.730
Fan Yu refused to give him to me.

42:32.840 --> 42:35.370
She said he's too young
and must stay with her.

42:36.970 --> 42:38.110
You... How dare you...

42:38.110 --> 42:38.710
Mother!

42:39.160 --> 42:40.110
Fan Yu was the one cheating!

42:40.110 --> 42:41.550
Why are you hitting me?

42:42.040 --> 42:43.120
You couldn't even

42:43.150 --> 42:44.410
keep a grandson for me!

42:44.420 --> 42:45.680
Yeah, I am hitting you!

42:45.950 --> 42:46.710
You loser!

42:46.920 --> 42:48.670
What sin did I commit?

42:49.110 --> 42:49.880
Why did I give birth

42:49.880 --> 42:51.880
to a lifetime loser

42:51.900 --> 42:54.010
like you?

42:54.230 --> 42:55.670
You loser!

42:57.200 --> 42:57.670
Yes.

42:58.590 --> 42:59.510
I am a loser.

43:00.190 --> 43:00.850
I'll leave.

43:01.630 --> 43:02.090
I'll go.

43:02.550 --> 43:03.400
I'm leaving!

43:03.770 --> 43:04.250
You...

43:04.510 --> 43:05.960
You... You go...

43:06.670 --> 43:09.070
You're actually leaving?

43:09.210 --> 43:11.710
You are a loser!
Why can't I call you that?

43:11.920 --> 43:13.360
I said you're a loser,

43:13.800 --> 43:15.000
and you're just a...

43:15.630 --> 43:17.100
Lo... Lo...

43:17.760 --> 43:18.360
Grandma!

43:18.630 --> 43:19.190
Grandma!

43:21.440 --> 43:22.070
Grandma!

43:36.320 --> 43:40.010
[Kong Island]
